txt.en: Brother! We are together, let us strike in unison!
I am with you Brother! We shall punish them together!
'You will taste of my rage for what you've done to my brother!'
I am here, Brother! You take the weak one and I'll take the ugly one!
'I feel my brother's pain. Now you will feel mine!'
'My brother! I will make them pay for wounding you!'
'We were bred for battle, we were bred as one!'
